{"tid":1965473,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google 獲准啟用太平洋光纖台灣段   香港段或因美國國安問題啟用無期","createTime":"2020-04-09T13:15:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-11T05:15:41.000Z","uid":31405,"like":32,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"90b4f21dfcea12c0c9cfeeb120c2df9fa51d1bd9","tid":1965473,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:15:53.000Z","msg":"美國司法部、國土安全部與國防部昨日（8 日）建議聯邦通信委員會（Federal Communications Commission，FCC）批准 Google 母公司 Alphabet Inc 的要求，啟用太平洋光纖網路（Pacific Light Cable Network System）當中連接加州與台灣的部分。<br />\n <br />\n跨太平洋海底光纖網路全長 8000 英里（約 1 萬 2875 公里），連往台灣與香港的部分早前已經完工，至今卻沒有啟用。這次經司法部與美國的其他機構的建議，聯邦通信委員會也同意准許 Google 營運這段線路半年，並等候許可證申請的最後安排。<br />\n <br />\nGoogle 在今年稍早告訴相關監管機關，迫切需要滿足美國與台灣之間的內部容量（connectivity capacity）需求，特別是要將 Google 在台灣的資料中心與在美國的資料中心連結，並服務整個亞太地區用戶。<br />\n <br />\n美國司法部最終告訴聯邦通信委員會，表示支持 Google 修改後的版本。<span style=\"color: red;\">而司法部與美國其他相關機構均認為，「批准一條直接連接美國與香港的電纜系統，將嚴重危害國家安全及美國的執法權益」，因此香港部分的海底電纜仍然遭到擱置，啟用無期。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/04/09/pcln-taiwan/life-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F04%2F09%2Fpcln-taiwan%2Flife-tech%2F&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVYbCTaNrw2SAqZBfI0xY0Mo%3D&h=ce0fac94\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/04/09/pcln-taiwan/life-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國慢慢切斷緊同香港既來往<br />\n照咁睇關係法真係會取消<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a33fe45fb1d15ec72c008882bff00bf1bc3fe9cf","tid":1965473,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:20:33.000Z","msg":"就快到終局<br />\n<br />\n香港人要加快手腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ba5395d8b4caa0c9aac00655c5e59d407f44c0","tid":1965473,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"其實連同唔連有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebfef05f7dbe4c7637fd90a1c2a667caa7624ac","tid":1965473,"uid":49044,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"47ba5395d8b4caa0c9aac00655c5e59d407f44c0","tid":1965473,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"其實連同唔連有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:23:31.000Z","msg":"由香港經歐州連去美國server 快，定經太平洋快啲?"},{"pid":"227963432e222d531bf4669520a70a77ed48142e","tid":1965473,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47ba5395d8b4caa0c9aac00655c5e59d407f44c0","tid":1965473,"uid":42340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:21:23.000Z","msg":"其實連同唔連有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:24:26.000Z","msg":"較早時間已經有人發現<br />\n有2個美國既網站香港既ip已經上唔到"},{"pid":"47af218db99d43282dde85b906ad11c45f0595c7","tid":1965473,"uid":49044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"姐係起撚左唔比用<br />\n咁美國真係去到盡喎 Google蝕到仆街"},{"pid":"eafeea6aefd0ef7e7c8c77f26879504b36b9f66d","tid":1965473,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:47:12.000Z","msg":"偽創科局仲聲稱要發展Data Centre<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6c4b9bee322de0816ac0a05cf15bdff951bb7f3","tid":1965473,"uid":42900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T14:55:24.000Z","msg":"起呢舊野要幾錢"},{"pid":"5ce642aee05e97988ffd65505aecb3f5936a069a","tid":1965473,"uid":24282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-11T05:15:41.000Z","msg":"連美國game server低ping d? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}